{"tid":2365120,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"光纖用Lan線問題","createTime":"2021-01-13T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T03:58:20.000Z","uid":6753,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"73889c7ca125eeb63ef8e4144c9aeb99e6eac9e0","tid":2365120,"uid":6753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"屋企 原本房同廳都有Lan port<br />\n但廳裝左光纖之後 廳個Lan port 就變左光纖盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAYhEzu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAYhEzu.jpg&h=bce90e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光纖盒駁modem modem駁router 全屋用wifi<br />\n<br />\n問題係最近喺房買左新電腦 想插lan線用（wifi 入到房收好慢）<br />\n直接插房個Lan port 無反應<br />\n想問是咪要重新拉過條新既暗線？（由modem拉入牆再入房？）<br />\n<br />\n如果係應該直接搵裝修師傅定寬頻公司？<br />\n<br />\nFYI，廳個Lan port 殘骸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21aWVbA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21aWVbA.png&h=79ae7deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3151eebfadeebb9d20a487537f1f8b37a5add73","tid":2365120,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"邊位師兄咁無手尾"},{"pid":"e7d6a44a4deeca885c7386a7494e401d4530c607","tid":2365120,"uid":255528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"拮落router咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eb4374aca6dd85b8fb8fcd1c0eaa71ee9f25d9","tid":2365120,"uid":6753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d6a44a4deeca885c7386a7494e401d4530c607","tid":2365120,"uid":255528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"拮落router咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"router 同modem都喺廳 電腦喺房"},{"pid":"36d1f1f23079c25337d57f795b0912a9b6ed173f","tid":2365120,"uid":6753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,