" />"},{"pid":"f3e10311224501d98725910fc6d927cbb8ea5d9f","tid":2365120,"uid":6753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"492e146639759bdea2e29d9079b8319280f4b98d","tid":2365120,"uid":209738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:34:38.000Z","msg":"咪搞個光纖盒，你應該從Modem或Router著手。在Modem同Router的Lan port拉線去電腦再分別測試網速。還有，你條lan線的製作標準同長度是亦會影響嗰速度。<br />\nlan線的製作標準參考：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LB4kGsw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLB4kGsw.jpg&h=942491a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"但都要經個光纖盒入返牆 再過房架？<br />\n<br />\n呢家計畫係<br />\n開光纖盒<br />\n搵返俾人剪左既lan頭<br />\n自己打頭<br />\n穿過個光纖盒（未用個啲窿）<br />\n直接吉入router/modem"},{"pid":"93a738e8615dfac8c168a22a531ad3d540707bb7","tid":2365120,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"你未整光纖之前應該係廳有條線插住連番你房個Lan port <br />\n個條線仲係唔係度 插落個router再入房試下"},{"pid":"896b57ae0389e8b89c464b002e21a0f5b54cb07d","tid":2365120,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"裝修師傅"},{"pid":"a72afac7b8b1490a98e28361ec81b14ffe067a5c","tid":2365120,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e4c6c47dc2d6f050112b0f616924dc33fc41fd","tid":2365120,"uid":6753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20c87cce078c846b57b90821527468a9205d7ce3","tid":2365120,"uid":40499,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c0878460a5b53b7e7c9ef8cb4961ec6197fec4d","tid":2365120,"uid":40826,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"咪害人啦 香港大部分樓都唔適合用homeplug"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"香港樓多數一層同一回路 點大部分唔適合 你唔好同我講買隻1000MB 比唔足呀 我好肯定佢一定好過用wifi入房"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T00:59:00.000Z","msg":"但有lan唔係都係用lan會好d咩？<br />\n用wifi又要買張wifi卡<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"pink\">同埋唔識嘢 硬係覺得lan 穩同快過wifi</span></span>"},"citedBy"